dct_title_s: Rand,McNally & Co.'s indexed atlas of the world map of South Africa
dct_description_sm: At top of map: Rand, McNally & Company's indexed atlas of the world. 546-547. Map of South Africa, showing portion of Damara Land and Great Namaqua Land; relief shown by hachures. Text on verso: South Africa. From: Rand, McNally & Co's indexed atlas of the world. Chicago, New York : Rand McNally & Co., 1892.
